                        </div>
                        <div class="photo-placeholder">
                            <img src="/assets/images/prayergarden3.jpg" alt="Cathcart UF prayer garden" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p>A quiet space for all to rest. All are welcome to have a walk around the garden, have a
                        rest and a bit of quiet time. We have seasonal topics on display for contemplation and to
                        pray over. We hope you will find the garden a helpful place!</p>

                    <div class="photo-row">
